626|"CHAPTER VII"|FALSE
626|"THE COMPLAINT OF BOOKS AGAINST WARS"|FALSE
626|"Almighty Author and Lover of peace, scatter the nations that delight in"|FALSE
626|"war, which is above all plagues injurious to books.  For wars being"|FALSE
